<text top="261" left="186" width="747" height="46" font="font2" id="p1_t3" reading_order_no="1" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">mistake,  “trade,  not  aid”  on  the  scale  of  the </text>
<text top="302" left="186" width="748" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t4" reading_order_no="2" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">U.N.  is  very  much a  business),  Cipriani  was  in </text>
